# Production: https://your-api.onrender.com (no trailing slash)
# Dev / vite preview: leave empty to use Vite proxy /api → localhost:3000 (API must be running).
# Vercel/static hosts: set this in build env or /api requests return index.html and break JSON parsing.
VITE_API_BASE_URL=

# Public web origin (no trailing slash). Set in production builds for absolute Open Graph / Twitter
# image URLs, og:url, and rel=canonical in index.html. Example: https://spirit-talker.example.com
# VITE_SITE_ORIGIN=

# Shown on Pay wall and legal pages (mailto). Example: support@yourdomain.com
# VITE_SUPPORT_EMAIL=

# Optional GA4: set to your Measurement ID (G-…) so `track` / EV* events forward after cookie consent.
# VITE_GA_MEASUREMENT_ID=
